{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":667,"text":"A few years ago, about seven years ago,"},{"time":2786,"text":"I found myself hiding\nin a festival toilet,"},{"time":6559,"text":"a music festival toilet,"},{"time":8382,"text":"and if anyone's been to a music festival,"},{"time":11533,"text":"yeah, you'll know that by the third day,"},{"time":15478,"text":"it's pretty nasty."},{"time":17191,"text":"I was standing in the toilet\nbecause I couldn't even sit down,"},{"time":20501,"text":"because the toilet roll had run out,"},{"time":23208,"text":"there was mud everywhere,"},{"time":24676,"text":"and it smelled pretty bad."},{"time":26125,"text":"And I stood there thinking,"},{"time":27926,"text":"\"What am I doing?\nI don't even need the toilet.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":30958,"text":"But the reason I went"},{"time":32340,"text":"was because I was volunteering\nfor a large charity on climate justice,"},{"time":36800,"text":"and it was seven years ago,"},{"time":38732,"text":"when lots of people didn't believe\nin climate change,"},{"time":41247,"text":"people were very cynical about activism,"},{"time":43176,"text":"and my role, with all of my teammates,"},{"time":45058,"text":"was to get people to sign petitions\non climate justice"},{"time":48083,"text":"and educate them\na bit more about the issue."},{"time":50661,"text":"And I cared deeply about climate change\nand lots of inequality,"},{"time":54582,"text":"so I'd go and I'd talk to lots of people,"},{"time":56559,"text":"which made me nervous\nand drained me of energy,"},{"time":59813,"text":"but I did it because I cared,"},{"time":61662,"text":"but I would hide in the toilets,\nbecause I'd be exhausted,"},{"time":65591,"text":"and I didn't want my teammates\ndoubting my commitment to the cause,"},{"time":69560,"text":"thinking that I was slacking."},{"time":71465,"text":"And we'd go and meet\nat the end of our shift,"},{"time":73632,"text":"and we'd count how many petitions\nhad been signed,"},{"time":76021,"text":"and often I'd win the amount\nof petitions signed"},{"time":78712,"text":"even though I had\nmy little breaks in the toilet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81275,"text":"But I was always very jealous\nof the other activists,"},{"time":84046,"text":"because either they had\nthe same amount of energy"},{"time":86434,"text":"as they had when they began the shift\nof getting people to sign petitions,"},{"time":91133,"text":"or often they had more energy,"},{"time":93101,"text":"and they'd be really excited about\ngoing to watch the bands in the evening"},{"time":96626,"text":"and having a dance."},{"time":97824,"text":"And even if I loved the bands,"},{"time":99959,"text":"all I wanted to do was to go back\nto my tent and have a sleep,"},{"time":103118,"text":"because I'd just feel\ncompletely wiped out,"},{"time":105809,"text":"and I was really jealous of people\nthat had the energy"},{"time":108390,"text":"to go and party hard at the festivals."},{"time":111703,"text":"But it also made me really angry,\nas well, inside."},{"time":114639,"text":"I thought, \"This isn't fair,\nI'm an introvert,"},{"time":117585,"text":"and all of the offline campaigning\nseems to be favoring extroverts.\""},{"time":123034,"text":"I would go on marches which drained me."},{"time":125256,"text":"That was the other option."},{"time":126542,"text":"Or I'd go and join campaigns\noutside embassies or shops."},{"time":130967,"text":"The only thing that was on offer\nwas around lots of people,"},{"time":133936,"text":"it was very loud activism,"},{"time":135912,"text":"it always involved lots of people,\nit was performing."},{"time":138959,"text":"None of it was for introverts,"},{"time":141214,"text":"and I not only thought\nthat that wasn't fair,"},{"time":143881,"text":"because a third to a half\nof the world's population are introverts,"},{"time":148731,"text":"which isn't fair on them,\nbecause we burn out,"},{"time":151770,"text":"or we'd be put off\nby activism and not do it,"},{"time":154351,"text":"and everyone needs to be\nan activist in this world."},{"time":158414,"text":"And also, I didn't think\nit was particularly clever,"},{"time":161080,"text":"but I could see that a lot\nof the activism that worked"},{"time":164835,"text":"wasn't only extrovert activism."},{"time":167106,"text":"It wasn't only the loud stuff."},{"time":168875,"text":"It wasn't about people\nperforming all the time."},{"time":171788,"text":"A lot of the work that was needed\nwas in the background,"},{"time":174433,"text":"was hidden, wasn't seen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177031,"text":"And when I ended up\njust being a campaigner,"},{"time":179443,"text":"because it's the only job\nI can do, really --"},{"time":181586,"text":"I was campaigning at university,"},{"time":183325,"text":"and for the last 10 years,\nI've been a professional campaigner"},{"time":186381,"text":"for large charities,"},{"time":187572,"text":"and now I'm a creative campaigner\nconsultant for different charities"},{"time":191445,"text":"as well as other work I do --"},{"time":193733,"text":"but I knew that there were other forms\nof activism that were needed."},{"time":197607,"text":"I started tinkering about seven years ago"},{"time":200187,"text":"to see what quieter forms of activism\nI could engage with"},{"time":203965,"text":"so I didn't burn out as an activist,"},{"time":206266,"text":"but also to look at some of the issues\nI was concerned about in campaigning."},{"time":211052,"text":"I was very lucky that, when I worked\nfor Oxfam and other big charities,"},{"time":214506,"text":"I could read lots of big reports"},{"time":216728,"text":"on what influenced\npoliticians and businesses"},{"time":220006,"text":"and the general public,"},{"time":221721,"text":"what campaigns worked really well,\nwhich ones didn't."},{"time":224223,"text":"And I'm a bit of a geek,\nso I look at all of that stuff,"},{"time":227182,"text":"and I wanted to tinker around"},{"time":228588,"text":"to see how I could engage people\nin social change in a different way,"},{"time":232477,"text":"because I think if we want the world\nto be more beautiful, kind and just,"},{"time":237096,"text":"then our activism\nshould be beautiful, kind and just,"},{"time":240913,"text":"and often it's not."},{"time":242723,"text":"And today, I just want to talk\nabout three ways"},{"time":245087,"text":"that I think activism needs introverts."},{"time":247597,"text":"I think there's lot of other ways,\nbut I'm just going to talk about three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251731,"text":"And the first one is:\nactivism is often very quick,"},{"time":255771,"text":"and it's about doing,"},{"time":257105,"text":"so extroverts, often their immediate\nresponse to injustice is,"},{"time":260384,"text":"we've got to do stuff now,"},{"time":261868,"text":"we've got to react really quickly --"},{"time":263702,"text":"and yes, we do need to react,"},{"time":265341,"text":"but we need to be strategic\nin our campaigning,"},{"time":267961,"text":"and if we just act on anger,"},{"time":269611,"text":"often we do the wrong things."},{"time":272177,"text":"I use craft, like needlework --"},{"time":274829,"text":"like this guy behind me is doing --"},{"time":276932,"text":"as a way to not only slow down\nthose extrovert doers,"},{"time":280790,"text":"but also to bring in nervous,\nquiet introverts into activism."},{"time":287216,"text":"By doing repetitive actions,"},{"time":289751,"text":"like handicraft, you can't do it fast,\nyou have to do it slowly."},{"time":292789,"text":"And those repetitive stitches"},{"time":294524,"text":"help you meditate on the big,\ncomplex, messy social change issues"},{"time":298612,"text":"and figure out what we can do"},{"time":300984,"text":"as a citizen, as a consumer,\nas a constituent,"},{"time":306413,"text":"and all of those different things."},{"time":308421,"text":"It helps you think critically\nwhile you're stitching away,"},{"time":311842,"text":"and it helps you be more mindful\nof what are your motives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314582,"text":"Are you that Barbie aid worker\nthat was mentioned before?"},{"time":317954,"text":"Are you about joining\npeople in solidarity,"},{"time":320629,"text":"or do you want to be the savior,\nwhich often isn't very ethical?"},{"time":323829,"text":"But doing needle work together, as well,"},{"time":326201,"text":"extroverts and introverts and ambivert --"},{"time":329892,"text":"everyone's on the scale\nin different places --"},{"time":332139,"text":"because it's a quiet,\nslow form of activism,"},{"time":336917,"text":"it really helps introverts be heard"},{"time":339711,"text":"in other areas, where\nthey are often not heard."},{"time":343603,"text":"It sounds odd,"},{"time":346277,"text":"but while you're stitching,\nyou don't need eye contact with people."},{"time":349929,"text":"So, for nervous introverts,"},{"time":352065,"text":"it means that you can stitch away\nnext to someone or a group of people"},{"time":356279,"text":"and ask questions that you're thinking"},{"time":358502,"text":"that often you don't\nget time to ask people,"},{"time":361589,"text":"or you're too nervous to ask\nif you give them eye contact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364510,"text":"So you can get introverts,\nwho are those big, deep thinkers,"},{"time":367486,"text":"saying, \"That's really interesting\nthat you want to do"},{"time":370677,"text":"that extrovert form of activism\nthat's about shaming people"},{"time":373917,"text":"or quickly going out somewhere,"},{"time":375632,"text":"but who are you trying to target and how,"},{"time":377830,"text":"and is that the best way to do it?\""},{"time":379783,"text":"So it means you could have\nthese discussions in a very slow way,"},{"time":382854,"text":"which is great for the extrovert\nto slow down and think deeply,"},{"time":385855,"text":"but it's really good\nfor the introvert as well,"},{"time":388086,"text":"to be heard and to feel\npart of that movement for change,"},{"time":391665,"text":"in a good way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392840,"text":"Some ways we do it is stitch cards"},{"time":395246,"text":"about what values we thread\nthrough our activism,"},{"time":398333,"text":"and making sure that we don't\njust react in unethical ways."},{"time":401865,"text":"One, sometimes we work\nwith art institutions"},{"time":404699,"text":"where we will get\nover 150 people at the V&amp;A"},{"time":407795,"text":"who can come for hours,"},{"time":409269,"text":"sit and stitch together\non a particular issue,"},{"time":411730,"text":"and then tweet what they're thinking\nor how it went, like this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415727,"text":"Also, I always think\nthat activism needs introverts"},{"time":418974,"text":"because we're really good\nat intimate activism."},{"time":422013,"text":"So we're good at slow activism,"},{"time":423664,"text":"and we're really good\nat intimate activism,"},{"time":425974,"text":"and if this year has told us anything,"},{"time":427840,"text":"it's told us that we need to,\nwhen we're engaging power holders,"},{"time":431705,"text":"we need to engage them by listening\nto people we disagree with,"},{"time":435039,"text":"by building bridges not walls --"},{"time":437169,"text":"walls or wars --"},{"time":439975,"text":"and by being critical friends,\nnot aggressive enemies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443371,"text":"And one example\nthat I do a lot with introverts,"},{"time":446269,"text":"but with lots of people,"},{"time":447444,"text":"is make gifts for people in power,"},{"time":449554,"text":"so not be outside screaming at them,"},{"time":452182,"text":"but to give them something\nlike a bespoke handkerchief"},{"time":455110,"text":"saying, \"Don't blow it."},{"time":456469,"text":"Use your power for good."},{"time":458000,"text":"We know you've got a difficult job\nin your position of power."},{"time":461175,"text":"How can we help you?\""},{"time":462937,"text":"And what's great is, for the introverts,"},{"time":465676,"text":"we can write letters\nwhile we're making these gifts,"},{"time":468136,"text":"so for us, Marks and Spencer,"},{"time":470533,"text":"we tried to campaign to get them\nto implement the living wage."},{"time":474978,"text":"So we made all the 14 board members\nbespoke handkerchiefs."},{"time":479044,"text":"We wrote them letters, we boxed them up,"},{"time":481360,"text":"and we went to the AGM\nto hand-deliver our gifts"},{"time":484417,"text":"and to have that form of intimate activism"},{"time":486937,"text":"where we had discussions with them."},{"time":489107,"text":"And what was brilliant\nwas that the chair of the board"},{"time":492314,"text":"told us how amazing our campaign was,"},{"time":494290,"text":"how heartfelt it was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496153,"text":"The board members, like Martha Lane Fox,"},{"time":498281,"text":"who has hundreds of thousands\nof followers on Twitter,"},{"time":501209,"text":"and highly influential in business,"},{"time":503511,"text":"tweeted how impressed she was,"},{"time":505559,"text":"and within 10 months,"},{"time":507170,"text":"we'd had meetings with Marks and Spencer"},{"time":509750,"text":"to say, \"We know this is difficult\nto be a living wage employer,"},{"time":513314,"text":"but if you can be one,"},{"time":514687,"text":"the rest of the sector will look at it,"},{"time":516570,"text":"and it's not right that some of your\namazing workers are working full time"},{"time":521196,"text":"and still can't pay their bills."},{"time":522759,"text":"And we love Marks and Spencer."},{"time":524283,"text":"How can you be the role model\nthat we want you to be?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":527829,"text":"So that was that intimate\nform of activism."},{"time":529862,"text":"We had lots of meetings with them."},{"time":532187,"text":"We then gave them Christmas cards\nand Valentine's cards to say,"},{"time":536710,"text":"\"We really want to encourage you\nto implement the living wage,"},{"time":540037,"text":"and within 10 months,\nthey'd announced to the media"},{"time":542869,"text":"that they were going to pay\nthe independent living wage, and now --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":546759,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548592,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549767,"text":"And now we're trying\nto work with them to be accredited,"},{"time":553330,"text":"which is really important,"},{"time":554633,"text":"and we went back to the last AGM this June"},{"time":557109,"text":"and we had these amazing one-to-one\ndiscussions with the board members,"},{"time":560729,"text":"who told us how much\nthey loved their hankies"},{"time":562850,"text":"and how it really moved them,\nwhat we were doing,"},{"time":565748,"text":"and they all told us that if we were\nstanding outside screaming at them"},{"time":569236,"text":"and not being gentle in our protest,"},{"time":571380,"text":"they wouldn't have even listened to us,"},{"time":573281,"text":"never mind had those discussions with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575332,"text":"And I think introverts\nare really good at intimate activism"},{"time":578714,"text":"because we like to listen,"},{"time":580079,"text":"we like one-to-ones,"},{"time":581460,"text":"we don't like small talks,"},{"time":582831,"text":"we like those big, juicy issues\nto discuss with people,"},{"time":586381,"text":"we don't like conflict,"},{"time":587921,"text":"so we avoid it at all costs,"},{"time":589712,"text":"which is really important when\nwe're trying to engage power holders,"},{"time":593025,"text":"not to be conflicting\nwith them all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596632,"text":"The third way I think activists\nare really missing out"},{"time":601350,"text":"if they don't engage introverts"},{"time":603244,"text":"is that introverts, like I said,\ncan be half of the world's population,"},{"time":608299,"text":"and most of us won't say\nthat we're introvert,"},{"time":611427,"text":"or we get embarrassed\nby saying what overwhelms us."},{"time":614645,"text":"So for me, a few years ago,"},{"time":616670,"text":"my mom used to send me\ntexts in capital letters --"},{"time":619787,"text":"and she can now do emojis\nand everything, she's fine --"},{"time":622961,"text":"but as soon as I'd see this text,"},{"time":624764,"text":"I'd wince and think, \"Ooh,\nit's capital letters, it's too much.\""},{"time":628408,"text":"And I'd have to ignore it to read\nthe lovely text she sent me."},{"time":631614,"text":"And that's a bit embarrassing,"},{"time":633121,"text":"to tell people that capital\nletters overwhelm you,"},{"time":636257,"text":"but we really need introverts\nto help us do intriguing activism"},{"time":641290,"text":"that attracts them\nrather than puts them off."},{"time":643877,"text":"We're put off by big\nand brash giant posters"},{"time":647354,"text":"and capital letters and explanation marks"},{"time":649886,"text":"telling us what to do\nand vying for our attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653332,"text":"So some of the things I do with people\naround the world who take part"},{"time":657154,"text":"is make small bits\nof provocative street art"},{"time":659520,"text":"which are hung off eye level, very small,"},{"time":662186,"text":"and they're provocative messages."},{"time":663988,"text":"They're not preaching at people\nor telling them what to do."},{"time":667297,"text":"They're just getting people\nto engage in different ways,"},{"time":669955,"text":"and think for themselves,"},{"time":671170,"text":"because we don't like\nto be told what to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673921,"text":"It might be wearing\na green heart on your sleeve"},{"time":676398,"text":"saying what you love\nand how climate change will affect it,"},{"time":679319,"text":"and we'll wear it,"},{"time":680501,"text":"and if people say,"},{"time":681707,"text":"\"Why are you wearing a green heart\nwith the word 'chocolate' on?\""},{"time":685065,"text":"and we can have those one-to-one\nintimate conversations and say,"},{"time":688255,"text":"\"I love chocolate."},{"time":689470,"text":"Climate change is going to affect it,"},{"time":691736,"text":"and I think there's lot of other things\nthat climate change will affect,"},{"time":695207,"text":"and I really want to make sure I'm part\nof the solution, not the problem.\""},{"time":698774,"text":"And then we deflect, because we don't\nlike to be the center of attention,"},{"time":702377,"text":"and say, \"What do you love\nand how will climate change affect it?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":706071,"text":"Or it might be shop-dropping\ninstead of shop-lifting,"},{"time":708858,"text":"where we'll make little mini-scrolls\nwith lovely stories on"},{"time":712739,"text":"about what's the story\nbehind your clothes."},{"time":715121,"text":"Is it a joyful story of how it's made,\nor is it a torturous one?"},{"time":719121,"text":"And we'll just drop them\nin little pockets in shops,"},{"time":721942,"text":"all lowercase, all handwritten,"},{"time":724201,"text":"with kisses and smiley faces in ribbon,"},{"time":727575,"text":"and then people are excited\nthat they found it."},{"time":730197,"text":"And we often drop them in unethical shops"},{"time":732583,"text":"or in front pockets,"},{"time":734701,"text":"and it's a way that we can do\noffline campaigning"},{"time":737970,"text":"that engages us and doesn't burn us out,"},{"time":740455,"text":"but also engages other people\nin an intriguing way online and offline."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747061,"text":"So I've got two calls to action,"},{"time":750233,"text":"for the introverts and for the extroverts."},{"time":753242,"text":"For the ambivert,"},{"time":754765,"text":"you're involved in all of it."},{"time":757055,"text":"For the extroverts, I want to say\nthat when you're planning a campaign,"},{"time":762025,"text":"think about introverts."},{"time":763565,"text":"Think about how valuable our skills are,\njust as much as extroverts'."},{"time":768017,"text":"We're good at slowing down\nand thinking deeply,"},{"time":770800,"text":"and the detail of issues,\nwe're really good at bringing them out."},{"time":774673,"text":"We're good at intimate activism,\nso use us in that way."},{"time":778752,"text":"And we're good at intriguing people"},{"time":781069,"text":"by doing strange little things that help\ncreate conversations and thought."},{"time":785803,"text":"Introverts, my call to action for you is,"},{"time":789023,"text":"I know you like being on your own,"},{"time":790825,"text":"I know you like being in your head,"},{"time":792700,"text":"but activism needs you,"},{"time":794621,"text":"so sometimes you've got to get out there."},{"time":796677,"text":"It doesn't mean that you've got\nto turn into an extrovert and burn out,"},{"time":800035,"text":"because that's no use for anyone,"},{"time":801631,"text":"but what it does mean"},{"time":802852,"text":"is that you should value the skills\nand the traits that you have"},{"time":806820,"text":"that activism needs."},{"time":808835,"text":"So for everyone in this room,"},{"time":810423,"text":"whether you're an extrovert\nor an introvert or an ambivert,"},{"time":814256,"text":"the world needs you now more than ever,"},{"time":817161,"text":"and you've got no excuse\nnot to get involved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":819922,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":821097,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}